There is an (old) doc about it on the main page.<br /><a href="http://nesdev.com/powerpad.txt" class="postlink">http://nesdev.com/powerpad.txt</a><br /><br />You get 2 bits per read on D3/D4, I think you strobe it once then read 8 times.  There's a code example in that doc too, but just ask if you have any problems.  I don't think many people have used it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Fri Sep 24, 2010 2:46 pm</p><hr />
